<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Monitor de Estrategia — 6 abril 2026 | Balanz Research</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--bg-primary:#0a0e1a;--bg-card:#111827;--border:#1e2a45;--accent-blue:#3b82f6;--accent-cyan:#06b6d4;--accent-emerald:#10b981;--accent-amber:#f59e0b;--accent-red:#ef4444;--accent-purple:#8b5cf6;--text-primary:#f1f5f9;--text-secondary:#94a3b8;--text-muted:#64748b;--gradient-blue:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#06b6d4)}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:var(--bg-primary);color:var(--text-primary);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}::-webkit-scrollbar{width:6px}::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg-primary)}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border);border-radius:3px}.ambient-bg{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;overflow:hidden;pointer-events:none}.ambient-bg::before{content:'';position:absolute;width:600px;height:600px;top:-200px;right:-200px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(59,130,246,0.08) 0%,transparent 70%);animation:float1 20s ease-in-out infinite}.ambient-bg::after{content:'';position:absolute;width:500px;height:500px;bottom:-100px;left:-100px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(6,182,212,0.06) 0%,transparent 70%);animation:float2 25s ease-in-out infinite}@keyframes float1{0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0)}50%{transform:translate(-80px,60px)}}@keyframes float2{0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0)}50%{transform:translate(60px,-80px)}}.container{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 20px 60px}.header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:20px 0 32px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:32px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px}.header-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px}.logo-mark{width:48px;height:48px;background:var(--gradient-blue);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:20px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-1px}.header-title h1{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.5px}.header-title p{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:2px;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace}.date-badge{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:8px 14px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);font-family:'Space Mono',monospace}.live-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:6px;animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.4}}.tabs{display:flex;gap:4px;margin-bottom:28px;background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:12px;padding:4px;border:1px solid var(--border);overflow-x:auto}.tab{padding:10px 20px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text-muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;white-space:nowrap;border:none;background:transparent;font-family:inherit}.tab:hover{color:var(--text-secondary)}.tab.active{background:var(--accent-blue);color:#fff}.sub-tabs{display:flex;gap:0;margin-bottom:24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);overflow-x:auto}.sub-tab{padding:10px 20px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text-muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;white-space:nowrap;border:none;background:transparent;font-family:inherit;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;position:relative;bottom:-1px}.sub-tab:hover{color:var(--text-secondary)}.sub-tab.active{color:var(--accent-cyan);border-bottom-color:var(--accent-cyan)}.section-title{font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:16px;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace}.kpi-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:12px;margin-bottom:32px}.kpi-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;transition:all 0.3s}.kpi-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent-blue);transform:translateY(-2px)}.kpi-label{font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:8px;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace}.kpi-value{font-size:28px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-1px}.kpi-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:4px}.kpi-change{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;margin-top:6px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px}.kpi-change.positive{background:rgba(16,185,129,0.12);color:var(--accent-emerald)}.kpi-change.negative{background:rgba(239,68,68,0.12);color:var(--accent-red)}.strategy-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(340px,1fr));gap:16px;margin-bottom:32px}.strategy-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:all 0.3s}.strategy-card:hover{border-color:rgba(59,130,246,0.4);transform:translateY(-2px)}.strategy-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px}.strategy-card.buy::before{background:var(--gradient-blue)}.strategy-card.hold::before{background:var(--accent-amber)}.strategy-card.rotate::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent-purple),var(--accent-cyan))}.strategy-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px}.strategy-class{font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--text-muted);font-family:'Space Mono',monospace}.strategy-signal{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px}.signal-buy{background:rgba(59,130,246,0.15);color:var(--accent-blue)}.signal-hold{background:rgba(245,158,11,0.15);color:var(--accent-amber)}.signal-rotate{background:rgba(139,92,246,0.15);color:var(--accent-purple)}.strategy-instrument{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin-bottom:10px}.strategy-rationale{font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text-secondary)}.strategy-metrics{display:flex;gap:16px;margin-top:16px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);flex-wrap:wrap}.strategy-metric{text-align:center;flex:1;min-width:60px}.strategy-metric-label{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:4px;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace}.strategy-metric-value{font-size:16px;font-weight:700}.table-wrapper{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:24px}.table-header-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:18px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.table-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:600}.table-subtitle{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);font-family:'Space Mono',monospace}table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}th{text-align:left;padding:12px 16px;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--text-muted);font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-weight:400}th.right,td.right{text-align:right}td{padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,42,69,0.5);font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}tr:hover td{background:rgba(59,130,246,0.04)}.bond-name{font-weight:600}.perf-positive{color:var(--accent-emerald)}.perf-negative{color:var(--accent-red)}.perf-muted{color:var(--text-muted)}.highlight-row td{background:rgba(59,130,246,0.06)}.highlight-row .bond-name{color:var(--accent-blue)}.chart-container{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:24px;margin-bottom:24px;position:relative}.chart-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px}.chart-subtitle{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:20px}.chart-canvas-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;height:420px}.chart-legend{display:flex;gap:24px;margin-top:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}.legend-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)}.legend-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%}.news-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:32px}@media(max-width:800px){.news-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}.news-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:20px}.news-card h3{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.4}.news-items{list-style:none}.news-item{padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,42,69,0.5);font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--text-secondary)}.news-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}.news-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;margin-right:8px;font-weight:600;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace}.tag-bcra{background:rgba(6,182,212,0.15);color:var(--accent-cyan)}.tag-fmi{background:rgba(139,92,246,0.15);color:var(--accent-purple)}.tag-macro{background:rgba(245,158,11,0.15);color:var(--accent-amber)}.tag-pol{background:rgba(239,68,68,0.12);color:var(--accent-red)}.tag-reg{background:rgba(16,185,129,0.12);color:var(--accent-emerald)}.calendar-date{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent-cyan)}.comp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:32px}.comp-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:16px;text-align:center;transition:all 0.3s}.comp-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent-blue)}.comp-country{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:6px;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace}.comp-spread{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}.comp-change{font-size:11px;font-weight:600}.tab-content{display:none}.tab-content.active{display:block;animation:fadeIn 0.3s ease}.sub-content{display:none}.sub-content.active{display:block;animation:fadeIn 0.3s ease}@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}.footer{text-align:center;padding:32px 0 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:40px}.footer p{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto}@media(max-width:600px){.header{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}.kpi-row{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.strategy-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.kpi-value{font-size:22px}.strategy-instrument{font-size:20px}.chart-canvas-wrap{height:320px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="ambient-bg"></div>
<div class="container">
  <header class="header">
    <div class="header-left">
      <div class="logo-mark">B</div>
      <div class="header-title"><h1>Monitor de Estrategia</h1><p>Balanz Research — Crédito soberano, tasas y FX</p></div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <a href="../index.html" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--accent-cyan);text-decoration:none;padding:8px 14px;border:1px solid var(--accent-cyan);border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;transition:all 0.2s" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(6,182,212,0.15)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='transparent'">← Último informe</a>
      <div class="date-badge"><span class="live-dot" style="background:var(--accent-amber)"></span>Archivo: 6 abril 2026</div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="tabs">
    <button class="tab active" onclick="showTab('overview',this)">Resumen</button>
    <button class="tab" onclick="showTab('strategy',this)">Estrategia</button>
    <button class="tab" onclick="showTab('rendimientos',this)">Rendimientos</button>
    <button class="tab" onclick="showTab('weekly',this)">Semana</button>
    <button class="tab" onclick="showTab('calendar',this)">Agenda</button>
  </div>

  <!-- RESUMEN -->
  <div class="tab-content active" id="tab-overview">
    <div class="section-title">Indicadores clave</div>
    <div class="kpi-row">
      <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Compras BCRA (5d)</div><div class="kpi-value" style="color:var(--accent-emerald)">US$529M</div><div class="kpi-sub">YTD: US$4.457M</div></div>
      <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Z-Spread Argentina</div><div class="kpi-value">635 <span style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted)">pbs</span></div><div class="kpi-change negative">&#9650; +35 pbs 1s</div></div>
      <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">CCL</div><div class="kpi-value">1.484</div><div class="kpi-change positive">+0,7% semanal</div></div>
      <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">IPC Mar (est. Balanz)</div><div class="kpi-value">3,2% <span style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted)">m/m</span></div></div>
      <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Pobreza 2S25</div><div class="kpi-value" style="color:var(--accent-emerald)">28,2%</div><div class="kpi-sub">Mínimo desde 2018</div></div>
      <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Liquidación agro Mar</div><div class="kpi-value" style="color:var(--accent-emerald)">US$2.03bn</div><div class="kpi-sub">Mayor desde 2022, +8% i.a.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-title">Z-Spreads: Argentina vs Comparables (pbs)</div>
    <div class="comp-grid">
      <div class="comp-card" style="border-color:var(--accent-blue)"><div class="comp-country">Argentina</div><div class="comp-spread" style="color:var(--accent-blue)">635</div><div class="comp-change negative">+35 1s</div></div>
      <div class="comp-card"><div class="comp-country">Angola</div><div class="comp-spread">521</div><div class="comp-change negative">+49 1s</div></div>
      <div class="comp-card"><div class="comp-country">Ecuador</div><div class="comp-spread">504</div><div class="comp-change negative">+22 1s</div></div>
      <div class="comp-card"><div class="comp-country">Pakistán</div><div class="comp-spread">479</div><div class="comp-change negative">-25 1s</div></div>
      <div class="comp-card"><div class="comp-country">Egipto</div><div class="comp-spread">442</div><div class="comp-change negative">+29 1s</div></div>
      <div class="comp-card"><div class="comp-country">El Salvador</div><div class="comp-spread">396</div><div class="comp-change negative">+32 1s</div></div>
      <div class="comp-card"><div class="comp-country">Nigeria</div><div class="comp-spread">348</div><div class="comp-change negative">+35 1s</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-title">Recomendaciones principales</div>
    <div class="strategy-grid">
      <div class="strategy-card buy"><div class="strategy-header"><span class="strategy-class">Ley Extranjera</span><span class="strategy-signal signal-buy">Mantener</span></div><div class="strategy-instrument">GD41</div><div class="strategy-rationale">Risk-off global afectó valuaciones, pero acumulación de reservas del BCRA (impulsada por commodities) debería sostener crédito. Curva opera 200-250 pbs sobre promedio B-. Posibles mejoras de rating y financiamiento bilateral como catalizadores.</div><div class="strategy-metrics"><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">Precio</div><div class="strategy-metric-value">67,9</div></div><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">TIR</div><div class="strategy-metric-value">10,5%</div></div><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">1s</div><div class="strategy-metric-value" style="color:var(--accent-red)">-1,0%</div></div><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">12m</div><div class="strategy-metric-value" style="color:var(--accent-emerald)">+21,7%</div></div></div></div>
      <div class="strategy-card rotate"><div class="strategy-header"><span class="strategy-class">Ley Local</span><span class="strategy-signal signal-rotate">Rotar</span></div><div class="strategy-instrument">AL30</div><div class="strategy-rationale">Rotar desde GD30. Spread de legislación 152 pbs no justificado. Captura compresión hacia B- y convergencia con Globales.</div><div class="strategy-metrics"><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">Precio</div><div class="strategy-metric-value">82,0</div></div><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">TIR</div><div class="strategy-metric-value">10,8%</div></div><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">1s</div><div class="strategy-metric-value" style="color:var(--accent-emerald)">+0,2%</div></div><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">Spread</div><div class="strategy-metric-value">152pb</div></div></div></div>
      <div class="strategy-card buy"><div class="strategy-header"><span class="strategy-class">Provinciales</span><span class="strategy-signal signal-buy">Compra</span></div><div class="strategy-instrument">SFD34</div><div class="strategy-rationale">Santa Fe: fundamentos sólidos, baja deuda/ingresos. Beneficio de compresión soberana hacia B-.</div><div class="strategy-metrics"><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">Ret. esperado</div><div class="strategy-metric-value" style="color:var(--accent-emerald)">16,3%</div></div></div></div>
      <div class="strategy-card buy"><div class="strategy-header"><span class="strategy-class">Boncer + Cobertura</span><span class="strategy-signal signal-buy">Mantener</span></div><div class="strategy-instrument">TZX28 + Rofex</div><div class="strategy-rationale">Retorno 9,8% USD desde feb. Tasas comprimieron más rápido de lo esperado. Preferimos cubrir riesgo cambiario con Rofex. Inflación implícita bajo proyecciones → CER.</div><div class="strategy-metrics"><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">TEA</div><div class="strategy-metric-value">6,7%</div></div><div class="strategy-metric"><div class="strategy-metric-label">3m</div><div class="strategy-metric-value" style="color:var(--accent-emerald)">+13,6%</div></div></div></div>
      <div class="strategy-card hold"><div class="strategy-header"><span class="strategy-class">Tasa Fija</span><span class="strategy-signal signal-hold">Neutral</span></div><div class="strategy-instrument">—</div><div class="strategy-rationale">Inflación proyectada por encima de implícitas → preferimos CER.</div></div>
      <div class="strategy-card buy"><div class="strategy-header"><span class="strategy-class">ROFEX / DL</span><span class="strategy-signal signal-buy">Cobertura</span></div><div class="strategy-instrument">Rofex</div><div class="strategy-rationale">Contratos Rofex más atractivos para cobertura. Riesgos de posiciones en pesos aumentaron con tasas más bajas y TC estable nominalmente.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ESTRATEGIA -->
  <div class="tab-content" id="tab-strategy">
    <div class="section-title">Detalle por clase de activo</div>
    <div class="news-grid">
      <div class="news-card"><h3 style="color:var(--accent-blue)">&#9679; Ley Extranjera — GD41</h3><ul class="news-items"><li class="news-item">Risk-off global afectó valuaciones, pero acumulación de reservas debería sostener crédito.</li><li class="news-item">BCRA tiene ventana de oportunidad en cosecha para acumular gran parte de US$13bn estimados para 2026.</li><li class="news-item">Curva opera 200-250 pbs sobre promedio B-.</li><li class="news-item">Posibles mejoras de rating y financiamiento bilateral como catalizadores.</li><li class="news-item">GD41 ofrece mayor upside si converge hacia B-.</li></ul></div>
      <div class="news-card"><h3 style="color:var(--accent-purple)">&#9679; Ley Local — AL30 (rotar desde GD30)</h3><ul class="news-items"><li class="news-item">Spread legislación cerró en 152 pbs — excesivo.</li><li class="news-item">Manejo de pasivos incluiría ambas legislaciones.</li><li class="news-item">AL30 captura compresión hacia B- y convergencia con Globales.</li><li class="news-item">AL29: spread más amplio (176 pbs), menor potencial por duración.</li></ul></div>
      <div class="news-card"><h3 style="color:var(--accent-emerald)">&#9679; Provinciales — SFD34</h3><ul class="news-items"><li class="news-item">Santa Fe: fundamentos sólidos, baja deuda vs ingresos.</li><li class="news-item">Historial crediticio consistente.</li><li class="news-item">Se beneficiaría de compresión soberana hacia B-.</li></ul></div>
      <div class="news-card"><h3 style="color:var(--accent-cyan)">&#9679; Deuda Local — TZX28 + Rofex</h3><ul class="news-items"><li class="news-item">Menos atractivo en carry post compresión de tasas.</li><li class="news-item">Retorno esperado menor, esperan depreciación del TC.</li><li class="news-item">Tasas por debajo del escenario dovish.</li><li class="news-item">Inflación implícita bajo proyecciones → mayor carry en CER.</li><li class="news-item">Liquidez: CER, en particular X29Y6 (cobertura inflación marzo ~3,2%).</li></ul></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RENDIMIENTOS -->
  <div class="tab-content" id="tab-rendimientos">
    <div class="sub-tabs">
      <button class="sub-tab active" onclick="showSubTab('soberanos',this)">Soberanos</button>
      <button class="sub-tab" onclick="showSubTab('subsoberanos',this)">Subsoberanos</button>
      <button class="sub-tab" onclick="showSubTab('deuda-local',this)">Deuda Local</button>
    </div>
    <div class="sub-content active" id="sub-soberanos">
      <div class="chart-container"><div class="chart-title">Curvas de Crédito Soberano</div><div class="chart-subtitle">TIR (%) vs Duration — 1 abril 2026</div><div class="chart-canvas-wrap" id="curveChart"></div><div class="chart-legend"><div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#3b82f6"></div>Globales (GD)</div><div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#06b6d4"></div>Bonares (AL)</div><div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#94a3b8"></div>BOPREAs</div><div class="legend-item" style="margin-left:auto;font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted)">★ = Recomendado</div></div></div>
      <div class="section-title">Globales (Ley Extranjera)</div>
